Summary: Simulation of the Giove Shielding around a Zinc crystal at the Chooz Near Site.
Date: 6/21/18
How To Run: (In a directory that also contains the ChoozSimulation)
       	  : mkdir build
	  : cd build
	  : cmake -DGeant4_DIR=/home/geant4-build/lib/Geant4-10.3.1/ ../ChoozSimulatoin
	  : make -jN
	  : cp -r ../ChoozSimulation/macros/ .
	  : cp -r ../ChoozSimulation/input_spectra/ .
	  : ./RicochetSim macros/joe_10Mev-50GeV_neutrons.mac

